parameter.value: Things aren’t good now with my husband,

parameter.value: I can’t help him with any of the work in the fields,

parameter.value: I can’t help him use anything heavy.

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: I don’t want to be intimate with him anymore.

parameter.value: I get dark patches in front of my eyes,

parameter.name: Text
